{"tid":1530602,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[譴責破壞] 港鐵重建計劃","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T19:31:11.000Z","uid":23046,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"451c390335505f6e6f1daf2d562227bb5482fa22","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:05:29.000Z","msg":"有鑑於近日多個車站遭受<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">暴徒</span></span>破壞<br />\n令市民交通不便<br />\n實在令人髮指<br />\n因此，我認為自己港鐵自己救自己保護<br />\n香港人係不能接受惡意破壞<br />\n<br />\n被破壞既設施包括：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入閘機</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">車門</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">月台幕門</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由此可見，站內既設備亦非常脆弱<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">暴徒</span></span>亦係睇中呢一點去攻擊<br />\n所以除左重建之外，仲要加固<br />\n<br />\n而我個人既建議係使用<span style=\"color: orange;\">水泥、<span style=\"color: red;\">澎脹發泡膠</span>、玻璃膠、油漆</span>等等...（個人唔係裝修/工程佬，所以唔太識用咩材料，但見裝修都係用呢d執加固，所以唯有比啲方向大家）<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MeJ12xs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMeJ12xs.jpg&h=863334c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=720iJqChtxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D720iJqChtxM&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FW9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=b811c524\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=720iJqChtxM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n有巴打建議大家千其唔好咁做，有樣野叫澎脹發泡膠，五金鋪賣一支40蚊左右，送支管，隊支管塞入面噴啲膠入去，之後啲膠就會喺入面<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">澎脹50倍同變硬</span></strong>，用過就知澎脹得勁快而且勁難清得乾淨，乜機都打柴啦。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以下係各項設施既建議修復方案：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入閘機</span></span><br />\n所有窿窿喇喇，以及有可能進入機品核心內部既窿，以防暴徒再giu開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jxSVnvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjxSVnvV.jpg&h=ef93a5c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/hk-rail/images/f/f2/ADM_Con-3.JPG/revision/latest?cb=20090701034323&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fhk-rail%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff2%2FADM_Con-3.JPG%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20090701034323%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=a1474cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幕門車門</span></span><br />\n以下有幾個方案<br />\n我地睇到有唔少市民唔小心漏左遮等等既物件係幕門既中間，令車門<span style=\"color: red;\">不能緊閉</span><br />\n為針對呢個情況，我地要幫幕門<span style=\"color: red;\">關上</span><br />\n所以建議既修復位置為：係<span style=\"color: green;\">幕門關上時</span>既門喇(即中央位置)及兩側，令門能<span style=\"color: red;\">緊緊並貼服地關上</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8jMCFd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8jMCFd.jpg&h=e1dd189f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但要留意，因為修復工程後，材料要時間乾，所以要預留車門，以免完全影響乘客去路<br />\n<br />\n其二，我地發現因為香港人非常喜歡番工，而且近日亦有不合作運動，令地鐵既擠塞程度增加，有好多人都比幕門夾親，所以我認為應該加長開門既時間，所以我地應該增設<span style=\"color: red;\">永久開放式幕門車卡</span>，加建既方式同上面差唔多，但要係<span style=\"color: green;\">幕門開</span>既時候做。而幕門後面亦有安全制，建設永久式開放幕門時亦將安全制改裝為永久開啟，加倍安全<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qf63E0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQf63E0k.jpg&h=d0139592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上兩個重建幕門方法可以配合使用。<br />\n<br />\n其三，<span style=\"color: green;\">月台既空隙</span>亦係非常非常危險，無論係小朋友差錯腳，跌左銀包，定有人惡意扔野落去，後果都可能不堪設想。所以！月台空隙一定要封，唔可以再比同類形事件再次發生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbVPAwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbVPAwn.jpg&h=bb33fee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條gap咁大，咁危險，要改喇！<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他設備要重建既，不能盡錄<br />\n<br />\n大概執行方法：<br />\n1. 雖要有乘客留意工作人員既動向，因為重建係自發性而且不需要被表揚及報答，係俠客之義<br />\n2.時間要夠早，就好似港鐵內部既維修都係半夜做，我地都要盡量唔影響到乘客，所以建議時間係頭班車時間。<br />\n3.放工路線要清晰同預先計劃，原因同1. 2.差唔多<br />\n4.基於以上，最後係be water。一次重建唔完就重建兩次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能有好多不足<br />\n但港鐵服務大眾咁多年<br />\n見到被破壞<br />\n實在係痛心<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才，各位請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌得細力d<br />\n<br />\n拿～mon po狗，以上內容都係學術討論咋 <br />\n唔好亂黎"},{"pid":"11e3b766adedcd9c7120e8d177e2b19505f7b7ec","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"仲有車廂重建<br />\n<br />\n呢排暴徒係咁施放太多不明氣體<br />\n建議車箱/車站既出風位都要封一封"},{"pid":"2f9b67e6f391ad043944be177037056a4f6bf972","tid":1530602,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HW4s6Kb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHW4s6Kb.jpg&h=88ac9ddc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad7dbcc16889a880ae44afab56459e15ab620411","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:08:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"705272d789636d7dfeb20ccf6540ee76b1990a37","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:08:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e52d899c5d5bf3f897b73fa67411e8e336905f02","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba16633600808ff0563aebb25ac9b2bc8602c4d9","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3255b9a6fe770b20ff66e8700c8370f23324aca0","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d93fb623e35001c4e63ec59fbefd5acabc20122","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5e528eaf14b27fa6b1de10a9a8d5c7ae01d7b56","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"開係學術台冇人睇？"},{"pid":"8bee8123280554df09afab1d6cba18499675e962","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:10:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1571d8304d898b1b2e9e2c5e3bdf99bd0153dfc","tid":1530602,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"e8ea1a804f7c222a45bf7605c0bd606a59528d0c","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"[譴責破壞] 港鐵重建計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530623\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530623</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n重開係時事台"},{"pid":"7ee17155506ebdddcc41ecf7f0c5326896ce27aa","tid":1530602,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:16:54.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"c09a7b4f98797478ccf0a2d7208f9e4dc9479b21","tid":1530602,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"膨脹發泡膠最L好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac896b24fbe05eaae7d2309a8ff1b182b922f94","tid":1530602,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c09a7b4f98797478ccf0a2d7208f9e4dc9479b21","tid":1530602,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:18:16.000Z","msg":"膨脹發泡膠最L好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"幫我去新post推兩野<br />\n學術台好似冇咩人睇"},{"pid":"30fc56047c0e710d62b4ed703a065621e7d54178","tid":1530602,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"pusg"}]}